  "description": "AGENT-EUDR-016: Country Risk Evaluator Agent -- composite country risk scoring, commodity-specific risk analysis, deforestation hotspot detection, governance index integration, due diligence classification, trade flow analysis, risk report generation, and regulatory update tracking",
